07/27/80	controlargument_list.compin

Syntax:  .ifi controlargument_list
     OR  .ifi ctlarg_list


Function:
This macro emits an control argument list label and prepares for a list
of control arguments.


Macro action:
1) inserts 24pt. of white space
2) emits the label "CONTROL ARGUMENTS" in 12pt.  Helvetica Bold Roman
   flush left, followed by white space appropriate for the device
3) sets the text indentation to the second level in preparation for the
   list of control arguments (see controlargument.compin.info concern-
   ing generation of the control arguments)

(END)
